articles.title: Asia stocks on guard for earnings, China economy surprises - Reuters
articles.description: Asian stocks traded cautiously on Monday as U.S. earnings season gets into full swing this week, while a raft of Chinese data will offer insight into how the world's second-largest economy is recovering.
